# Writing

Draft all repo docs per `WRITING.md`.

Prefer `ai/skills/writing-standard/SKILL.md`. Voice: `reference/voice.md` (skill points there via `references/voice.md`).

When the skill is not loaded, enforce `WRITING.md` self-check before finishing any edit under `world/`, `templates/`, `playbook/`, `projects/`, `ai/` (non-skill), or root docs.

Do not rewrite `theory/`. Do not match treatise prose when drafting canon.

`world/` stays thin: frontmatter + fill sections only. Never paste Purpose, Theory, AI Prompt, or Review Checklist into `world/`. Never reset world by copying thick templates.
